{"tid":1380517,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發覺好多同路人法律意識好薄弱","createTime":"2019-07-29T04:50:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T07:15:01.000Z","uid":37537,"like":282,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"70e30e64fb8a829f438cc49e434bd6ee2a5857a5","tid":1380517,"uid":37537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:50:03.000Z","msg":"經過七仔同肥師奶事件之後<br />\n見到香港人開始知自己的法律權利<br />\n但我仍然見到佢地有做得不足之處<br />\n所以想係呢道重新提醒大家<br />\n大家有問題亦可以問<br />\n<br />\n利申:唔是律師,只係睇左好多police encounter的教育短片,想係道歸納總結下<br />\n<br />\n1.面對狗隻/疑似狗隻,第一件事要做的係冷靜淡定,亦要保持一個心態:狗做緊的工作即使係同自己利益有對立,仍然尊重,避免事情升溫同肢體接觸,最好同狗講英文,迫佢地用下個腦,令佢地行為冷靜理性啲<br />\n2.核實狗隻身份: Please show your valid police ID. I can't cooperate unless I know you are a real police officer. 不斷重複呢兩句直至見到ID為止<br />\n3.需要畀身份證或護照,但唔需要做任何其他野,包括答問題: Here is my ID. I am not discussing my day. I don't answer questions. I invoke the right to remain silent.<br />\n4.雖則唔好有肢體接觸,但要口頭上拒絕一切搜查/移動要求: I do not consent to any searches. I do not consent to move unless detained.<br />\n5.萬一被夾硬搜身搜出任何不利自己的物品,唔使驚,STFU (Shut the fuck up): I invoke the right to remain silent.<br />\n6.隨時確認自己係咪走得: Am I detained or am I free to go?<br />\n<br />\n唔使驚&quot;阻差辦工&quot;,你無肢體接觸,只係重申自己的權利的話係唔會阻到<br />\n唔使驚畀狗搜到任何野入罪,只要你唔consent搜身搜車,啲狗就係非法搜查,搵到的任何證據都係&quot;毒樹果&quot;,不能成為呈堂證供,加上你STFU,佢地就無辦法從你口中套料<br />\n<br />\n最後最重要:STFU!"},{"pid":"e552fc74f1258bca1b8a2755e5345c894e9fcbf9","tid":1380517,"uid":20379,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:51:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好型"},{"pid":"16f0f2e60f34919cecfe97268f59770d640aa608","tid":1380517,"uid":7818,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:52:47.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗報埋PGO叫佢拎ID"},{"pid":"5a69d541cc6e90d7344b9910ef8526bc46691c06","tid":1380517,"uid":37537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e552fc74f1258bca1b8a2755e5345c894e9fcbf9","tid":1380517,"uid":20379,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:51:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好型"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:53:24.000Z","msg":"要記住STFU!"},{"pid":"74fca6a28627a6ec29cb8a99965a1679650148be","tid":1380517,"uid":259092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:54:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bda1bc48e8d4e503a0ed40c77e0f3912a758ad28","tid":1380517,"uid":37537,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"16f0f2e60f34919cecfe97268f59770d640aa608","tid":1380517,"uid":7818,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:52:47.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗報埋PGO叫佢拎ID"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:55:19.000Z","msg":"你鍾意<br />\n如果你熟點玩的話可以<br />\n但唔報都無損失<br />\n總之只同有核實身份的狗隻合作<br />\n<br />\n補充:最緊要有拍片"},{"pid":"91a2dcadf535472df74ba43791eca025dd77f12c","tid":1380517,"uid":199257,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:55:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18202b35ada72d921116eaed21ff2a34630be2c0","tid":1380517,"uid":188337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:56:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a5a8452cf931a2cc99c2c0a6d7241f12ed0c03bc","tid":1380517,"uid":265113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:57:46.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"520df07d9df8f71fb5a9cdbc1615b6fc640d1b95","tid":1380517,"uid":44870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:59:01.000Z","msg":"不能只有我看到"},{"pid":"d183d019d32ebc876765bea6e0c09efc935ccf8b","tid":1380517,"uid":7818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201