re":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:08:30.000Z","msg":"救救手足，助手足免疫於偽中立深藍的語言暴力，殺人於無形。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1380120/page/5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1380120/page/5</a>"},{"pid":"7e347f2dd5a3ec1a61e06cb85985136e3659a9db","tid":1380517,"uid":37537,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9e48c6ffa6bd769f0fb33a5692abb0d25b2d9d07","tid":1380517,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:05:24.000Z","msg":"唔好行前,企直個人唔好屈身,狗會屈你襲狗搶槍"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:09:58.000Z","msg":"講開呢點可以講埋<br />\n除非佢地話明拘捕你,否則你係唔需要跟佢地指示去移動: I do no consent to move unless detained.<br />\n同時唔好有突然的動作,雙手隨時要畀狗隻見到,咁佢地就無藉口話你有危險舉動"},{"pid":"b1c8152be0004124a3037070d77e878f298d3182","tid":1380517,"uid":37537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"034b9fef25830cefcc50ea9362d1b7abc9a29abd","tid":1380517,"uid":41116,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:06:47.000Z","msg":"終審法院已經判左保持緘默糾正警察錯誤等等都唔係阻差辦公<br />\n<br />\n沉日d狗用要調查案件為由想無法庭手令無業主或佔用人許可下進入私人地方(開放比公眾出入唔等如係公眾地方)係戇鳩，7仔哥哥無做錯到<br />\n警察通例第44章有清楚寫明"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:12:17.000Z","msg":"佢地疑似想用&quot;hot pursuit&quot;來做warrant exception<br />\n所謂hot pursuit係當狗見到有人當下明顯犯左刑事罪行要當下追捕制伏,普通懷疑集結完全唔啱用<br />\n簡單來講,只要市民唔肢體接觸啲狗,只係不斷口頭重申自己權利係唔會有任何法律後果<br />\n<br />\nHot Pursuit<br />\nA doctrine that provides that the police may enter the premises where they suspect a crime has been committed without a warrant when delay would endanger their lives or the lives of others and lead to the escape of the alleged perpetrator; also sometimes called fresh pursuit."},{"pid":"c788aff2f1edad09c14e1629c7b39d1b2dbb2176","tid":1380517,"uid":37537,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d5c5472bd24ab35cee3dafc20fcc7a2f41ea2d37","tid":1380517,"uid":260181,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:08:09.000Z","msg":"呢位市民，你冇權睇我身分證"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:1