":1,"quote":{"pid":"f30ab25e16c5809b8538f62b11d31d6bcb4f05eb","tid":1380517,"uid":42521,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:42:34.000Z","msg":"咁俾身份證佢check, 唔答任何問題，唔俾搜袋<br />\n佢有冇法律理據拘捕/扣押你48小時?<br />\n佢要講明係拘捕先可以帶你走?<br />\n<br />\n如在查身份證，搜查隨身物件之前/途中，黑警自行釋法/誤導市民，係咪可以打搜證程序失當?<br />\n例如黑警好鍾意講阻差扮工，如一般市民唔清楚了解自己既權利，因黑警恐嚇之下俾佢搜左袋，咁又點分係主動配合調查定喺威脅之下被逼?<br />\n<br />\n如黑警無法提供合理理由去截查你，你拒絕出示身份證又是否犯法?<br />\n而所謂合理理由係要上到庭由法官/裁判官決定?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:55:31.000Z","msg":"佢係可以拉你扣你48H,由佢話拉你開始計<br />\n只有佢拉你的時候先唔需要你consent而可以移動你<br />\n所以,I do not consent to move unless detained!<br />\n<br />\n絕對係,無consent的話,佢地的搜查全屬非法(除非有warrant,咁就唔使consent)<br />\n所以, I do not consent to any searches!<br />\n<br />\n記住狗係可以合法地講大話!!!所以唔好畀佢地大到,唔好畀任何consent!!!<br />\n<br />\n係香港,查身份證唔使理由<br />\n係美國先要<br />\n不過有合理理由出示唔到身份證係OK,例如搵唔到,可能啱啱發現唔見左"},{"pid":"d1270bdb60e5c8b11f82d9ffeea73bc4aac58312","tid":1380517,"uid":37537,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1717ad95ae362f855baa2d3dd100d4dfe3432e7b","tid":1380517,"uid":59891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:30:12.000Z","msg":"搜野果度真係難唔俾佢搜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:56:38.000Z","msg":"唔consent<br />\n但唔好肢體阻礙佢地<br />\n由得佢地非法搜查,搜到把日本刀都告唔到你,只要你STFU"},{"pid":"d5d199049a15a67444fb5794768c03ed3ff6d516","tid":1380517,"uid":37537,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T20:36:19.000Z","msg":"重有樣野好有趣<br />\ndetain(拘留)同arrest(逮捕)權利上都有分別<br />\ndetain就最出名的48H同埋一樣唔可以搜身搜車搜屋,去到狗屋仍然要重申同行使自己權利<br />\n1. I invoke the right to remain silent.<br />\n2. I do not consent to any searches.<br />\n任何文件都係唔需要簽,不過上庭日期通知就即使簽都唔大問題<br />\n而detain只係需要reasonable suspicion,簡單講即係隻狗覺得你有屎<br />\n<br />\narrest就唔同,啲狗可以任搜同長期拘留你,而唔需要攞你consent<br />\n所以啲狗問得你的話,一定要say no<br />\n有趣地arrest係需要probable cause,即係佢地要有人證/物證先拘捕得人<br />\n如果你係detain期間畀左consent佢地search你或者透露左任何資料,咁佢地就可以根據啲料去arrest你,跟住再search勁啲<br />\n所以detain期間一定唔可以畀任何consent同答任何問題<br />\nNO CONSENT!!! STFU!!!"},{"pid":"59c4a8b6844f819cac4c9a46f741e7307eacee1f","tid":1380517,"uid":37537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T20:36:42.000Z","msg":"巴打記得背熟哂呢個post所有英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"133df9d9f477b3b08a3a33f7b88619f67df10cbd","tid":1380517,"uid":230662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T20:51:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JTurSi0LhJs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJTurSi0LhJs&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67Q3x%2FUg%2Bgbtl8eFt0uNm3qw%3D&h=1d0a2e80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JTurSi0LhJs</a>"},{"pid":"14b3c36921fd1c849b5027fdf6e5ba95574af45a","tid":1380517,"uid":37537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T20:51:55.000Z","msg":"記住<br />\n狗係幽靈,係吸血鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你口頭上答應/邀請左佢地就大撚鑊!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ad706b18939f267958afdfe3a6128a951dcda30","tid":1380517,"uid":37537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"133df9d9f477b3b08a3a33f7b88619f67df10cbd","tid":1380517,"uid":230662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T20:51:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JTurSi0LhJs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJTurSi0LhJs&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67Q3x%2FUg%2Bgbtl8eFt0uNm3qw%3D&h=1d0a2e80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JTurSi0LhJs</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T20:52:08.000Z","msg":"exactly!!!"},{"pid":"bf83409c6358f0328d67f537c9bdba9abc69a25d","tid":1380517,"uid":266968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T22:24:39.000Z","msg":"如果落單左被搜，拍片佢話唔比拍，或話再拍告阻差辦工點拆<br />\n<br />\n同埋七仔哥哥個到是咪真係可以强行入去搜，因為入面好多黑衫"},{"pid":"47fff7d09212